14:05.578 --> 14:07.313 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
PAUL CASALE, PROFESSOR,
UNIVERSITY OF UTAH
COLLEGE OF LAW: Well, I think
he'’s been

14:07.346 --> 14:10.149 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
