17:32.551 --> 17:34.387 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
window.

17:34.420 --> 17:41.427 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, people in positions of
power, people in
leadership positions, I hold to
a higher standard

17:41.460 --> 17:47.700 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
